{
  "info": {
    "name": "EclipseProtocol API",
    "_postman_id": "eclipse-protocol-collection",
    "description": "Coleção completa da API EclipseProtocol - FIAP\n\nOrdem sugerida para testar:\n1. POST /usuarios (sem token)\n2. POST /auth/login → salve o token na variável {{token}}\n3. POST /localizacoes\n4. POST /propriedades (usa idUsuario + idLocalizacao)\n5. POST /plantacoes (usa idPropriedade)\n6. POST /sensores (usa idPlantacao)\n7. POST /leituras (usa idSensor)\n8. POST /alertas (usa idLeitura + idPlantacao)\n9. POST /satelites\n10. POST /lixo-espacial\n11. POST /imagens-satelite (usa idSatelite + idPlantacao)\n12. POST /riscos-orbitais (usa idSatelite + idLixoEspacial)\n\nATENÇÃO - Riscos Orbitais usa CHAVE COMPOSTA:\n  GET/PUT/DELETE: /riscos-orbitais/{idSatelite}/{idLixoEspacial}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 - Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"gustavo.gomes@email.com\",\n  \"senha\": \"senha123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
